Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是雪雪太貪心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿栗子撿個不停才弄得這麼晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是無可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫我家是大家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋媽媽太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不得不照料大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕個什麼勁兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是隻鳥罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個羽毛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:18.96,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找到 藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上都不休息地反覆揮刀  真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兒時養成的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且呢  不好好練習的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一有一天能離開這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個人我是無論如何都想贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腋下太松垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  我去河邊洗臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能早點回去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然希望行人無法回去  一直留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是打得稍稍重了點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安啊雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早要到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南邊和西邊的交界處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了看到了 雪乃我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鳥啊  藍色的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是證據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我在南邊的森嶺撿栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的途中不經意間看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是至今還沒被人見到過真面目的那隻傳說中的藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這個是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多別的擁有藍色羽毛的鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是綾音故意塗上色做的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為動物博士的我都沒看到過的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有這麼美麗的羽毛的藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想見見它並和它成為朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  所以小鈴姐你也一起幫我找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不和行人說一下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔兔去把行人帶到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天還要去撿柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴去找藍鳥了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的藍鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Unidentified Mysterious Animal  未確認動物）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島上也有UMA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未被確認的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未被發現的新種類的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  對我來說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也稱得上是未知的珍獸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是行人你不是對不可靠的事物都持否定的態度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UMA和其他的是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在理論上是可以解釋的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  聽說如果能抓住藍鳥就能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來叫行人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一會再去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天必須去撿柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿小鈴沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然丟下了撿柴的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪雪硬把她帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙撿柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在行人正一個人撿著柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到藍鳥的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快開始搜索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有鷹鷹和貓頭鷹在就輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是它們昨晚就和媽媽一起去山上泡溫泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回到家的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下了「我們去溫泉了」的紙條
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡早上睡懶覺  早上喝酒和早上泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是一個廢柴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把女兒丟下不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就只靠我們幾個人找出藍鳥好好地炫耀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑藉這個氣味去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似只是羽毛進了鼻子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經受潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下了雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說小鈴  再到更深處去看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  小鈴沒有一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想一下的話  自從到了島上我們大多數時間都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我給小鈴添了這麼多的麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都讓她這麼費心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒幫上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是輕易能找到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是所謂的虛幻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  能找到藍鳥的話就能帶來幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是童話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小的時候千影姐姐經常讀給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能帶來幸福只限於童話中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我當然知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來只限於童話故事中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是與未知的動物交朋友這點不就足夠幸福了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是雪雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是藍鳥真的能帶來幸福的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐想要怎樣的幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話  一直維持現在的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  只要大家都能健健康康的就算幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一塊的氣味很重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇到它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要悄悄地接近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是沒見過的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完全都看不出是藍顏色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂跑一氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鳥  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有深溝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚才回來對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直找不到合適的柴火…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐你快起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃你早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說早安的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們掉到深溝裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為雪雪暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能爬得上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳腫起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是掉下來的時候扭到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很痛的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不礙事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 腳是這種情況要爬上去是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊緣太松了  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊緣比我想像的還要脆弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是行人的話  在這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  已經讓兔兔去通知行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人應該已經察覺到我們出事了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來找我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裡可是森林的最深處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有發現這個洞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排鼻子很靈敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人腦袋很好使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  雪乃她們沒在小鈴家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴也沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道在山裡出了什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道會這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就帶他們一起去泡溫泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能冷靜的下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家出了什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼不測  這是什麼話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全陷入混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情緒變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去山上找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡小姐就在村子裡找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野豬和貓頭鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去幫助行人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天見到藍鳥的就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是小鈴她們身邊發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是在森林中迷路了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了炸豬排  到你出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照氣味去尋找小鈴她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小鈴那邊也有鼻子很靈的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是因為迷路的話不會回不來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是遇到了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天徹底黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了櫻桃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特地摘給行人和炸豬排的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家分著吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊  行人他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟去哪找了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐你還真沉著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我緊張地受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也有被困在洞中的情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候行人很沉著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在想  要是我也能冷靜下來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會有辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐真堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和小鈴姐一起真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你什麼都會做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在我這個年紀已經在那個家裡獨自生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想像小鈴姐那麼堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的氣味會被沖走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最糟的情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排  野豬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨聲太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音似乎也傳的不遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴現在一定是忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才好像有誰在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想讓我跟著你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道小鈴她們在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給人帶來幸福的藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不相信這種迷信的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我小鈴在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會跟丟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鈴的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  我們在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人來救我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  藍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  到哪去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得安寧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會掉到那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴也真是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛  只要沒事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了防止再有人掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做一個柵欄之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為這個笨蛋才讓你遇到這麼大的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能再小心點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴還真是可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也給我學著點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  還真是個小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像我這樣綁根安全繩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很危險的 綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有一個白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  一起吃我帶來慰問大家的溫泉饅頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我們也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你擔心真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了傷不能隱瞞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我這麼見外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  腳很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變得孤零零的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都對我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而沒有一個人斥責過我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  行人你說我們是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴又小又輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家都說小鈴很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴一直都是盡力地在勉強著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是既怕孤獨又膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠保護小鈴
