Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.45,0:22:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人的背  好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人是重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  炸豬排也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直  一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的時光能一直繼續下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
